data.description: Beautiful well maintained home in Craftsbury Village Subdivision in Bono!!! This home has 4 bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms! A spacious living room with an electric fireplace and surround sound installed! The kitchen has great cabinet space with a large breakfast bar! The master suite offers a walk in closet with a double sink vanity and jetted tub and shower! There is a separate laundry room and a two car garage! Feel free to call and schedule a private tour of this beautiful home.
